  <scopecontent id="aspace_64c00d6e3832af77c203e8097a634af7">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>The records of Zion Episcopal Church of Palmyra document the activities of the church administration and give statistical information concerning the parishioners. Included in the collection is one volume (1823- 95) containing information on marriages, baptisms, confirmations, burials, communicants, and newspaper coverage of parish events. One volume of vestry minutes (1827-1917) contains entries of official church functions, financial matters and notes of elections to various offices. A third group of records is a series of annual sermons from 1852-61.</p>  </scopecontent>
